  ('1', '1 - 2', '2008', '14', '╨Ы╨╡╤Б╨╛╨▓╤К╨┤╤Б╨║╨░ ╨╝╨╕╤Б╤К╨╗', 'Forestry Ideas', '<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">╨Я╨а╨Ю╨г╨з╨Т╨Р╨Э╨Ш╨п ╨Т╨к╨а╨е╨г ╨а╨Р╨б╨в╨Х╨Ц╨Р ╨Э╨Р ╨а╨Р╨Ч╨Ы╨Ш╨з╨Э╨Ш ╨Я╨а╨Ю╨Ш╨Ч╨е╨Ю╨Ф╨Ш ╨Э╨Р ╨Ю╨С╨Ш╨Ъ╨Э╨Ю╨Т╨Х╨Э╨Р ╨Х╨Ы╨Р (ABIES ALBA MILL.) ╨Т ╨Ю╨Я╨Ш╨в╨Э╨Ш ╨Х╨Ъ╨Ю╨Ы╨Ю╨У╨Ш╨з╨Э╨Ш ╨Ъ╨г╨Ы╨в╨г╨а╨Ш ...................................................................................................................................3<br><em>╨Ш╨▓╨░╨╜ ╨Х╨▓╤В╨╕╨╝╨╛╨▓, ╨Т╨╡╨╗╨╕╤З╨║╨╛ ╨У╨░╨│╨╛╨▓</em></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>╨д╨Ы╨Ю╨а╨Э╨Ш ╨Х╨Ы╨Х╨Ь╨Х╨Э╨в╨Ш ╨Ш ╨С╨Ш╨Ю╨Ы╨Ю╨У╨Ш╨з╨Х╨Э ╨б╨Я╨Х╨Ъ╨в╨к╨а ╨Э╨Р ╨У╨Ю╨а╨Ш ╨б ╨Я╨а╨Х╨Ю╨С╨Ы╨Р╨Ф╨Р╨Т╨Р╨Э╨Х ╨Э╨Р ╨Ъ╨Ю╨б╨Ь╨Р╨в ╨Ф╨к╨С (QUERCUS PUBESCENSWILLD.)&#160; ╨Т ╨Ч╨Р╨Я╨Р╨Ф╨Э╨Ш╨в╨Х ╨У╨а╨Р╨Э╨Ш╨з╨Э╨Ш ╨Я╨Ы╨Р╨Э╨Ш╨Э╨Ш ..............................12<br><em>╨У╨╡╨╛╤А╨│╨╕ ╨У╨╛╨│╤Г╤И╨╡╨▓</em></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>╨Т╨к╨Ч╨б╨в╨Р╨Э╨Ю╨Т╨п╨Т╨Р╨Э╨Х ╨Э╨Р ╨Ю╨Я╨Ю╨Ц╨Р╨а╨Х╨Э╨Ш ╨У╨Ю╨а╨б╨Ъ╨Ш ╨Я╨Ы╨Ю╨й╨Ш ╨Э╨Р ╨в╨Х╨а╨Ш╨в╨Ю╨а╨Ш╨п╨в╨Р ╨Э╨Р ╨Ф╨У╨б тАЮ╨и╨Ш╨а╨Ю╨Ъ╨Р ╨Ы╨к╨Ъ╨РтАЭ<br>╨Ш ╨Ф╨У╨б тАЮ╨Ш╨Т╨Р╨Щ╨Ы╨Ю╨Т╨У╨а╨Р╨ФтАЭ ...............................................................................................29<br><em>╨Ъ╤А╨░╤Б╨╕╨╝╨╕╤А╨░ ╨Я╨╡╤В╨║╨╛╨▓╨░, ╨Р╨╗╨╡╨║╤Б╨░╨╜╨┤╤К╤А ╨в╨░╤И╨╡╨▓, ╨Ы╨░╤В╨╕╨╜╨║╨░ ╨в╨╛╨┐╨░╨╗╨╛╨▓╨░-╨Ц╨╡╨╢╨╕╤Е╨░</em></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>╨Р╨Э╨Р╨Ы╨Ш╨Ч ╨Ш ╨Ю╨ж╨Х╨Э╨Ъ╨Р ╨Э╨Р ╨Я╨Ю╨Ц╨Р╨а╨Ш╨в╨Х ╨Ш ╨Я╨Ю╨Ц╨Р╨а╨Э╨Р╨в╨Р ╨Ю╨Я╨Р╨б╨Э╨Ю╨б╨в ╨Т ╨У╨Ю╨а╨Ш╨в╨Х .....................................................................................................................................30<br></span><em><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">╨Ъ╨╕╤А╨╕╨╗ ╨Ы╤О╨▒╨╡╨╜╨╛╨▓, ╨Т╨╗╨░╨┤╨╕╨╝╨╕╤А ╨Ъ╨╛╨╜╤Б╤В╨░╨╜╤В╨╕╨╜╨╛╨▓</span></em></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>╨Ъ╨Ш╨б╨Х╨Ы ╨Ф╨а╨Х╨Э╨Р╨Ц ╨Э╨Р ╨Э╨Р╨б╨Ш╨Я╨Э╨Ш ╨б╨г╨С╨б╨в╨а╨Р╨в╨Ш</span></span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"> ╨Ю╨в ╨Ф╨Ю╨С╨Ш╨Т ╨Э╨Р ╨Ю╨Ы╨Ю╨Т╨Э╨Ю-╨ж╨Ш╨Э╨Ъ╨Ю╨Т╨Р ╨а╨г╨Ф╨Р .......................................................................................................................................47<br><em>╨а╨╛╤Б╨╕╤Ж╨░ ╨Я╨╡╤В╤А╨╛╨▓╨░</em></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>╨Я╨а╨Ю╨Ф╨г╨Ъ╨в╨Ш╨Т╨Э╨Ю╨б╨в ╨Э╨Р ╨д╨Х╨а╨Ь╨Х╨а╨Э╨Ю ╨Ю╨в╨У╨Ы╨Х╨Ц╨Ф╨Р╨Э╨Ш ╨Я╨Ю╨Ы╨б╨Ъ╨Ш ╨п╨а╨Х╨С╨Ш╨ж╨Ш (PERDIX PERDIX L.) ╨Т ╨Ч╨Р╨Т╨Ш╨б╨Ш╨Ь╨Ю╨б╨в ╨Ю╨в ╨Э╨п╨Ъ╨Ю╨Ш ╨д╨Р╨Ъ╨в╨Ю╨а╨Ш ╨Э╨Р ╨б╨а╨Х╨Ф╨Р╨в╨Р ..............................................................74<br></span><em><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">╨Ч╨▓╨╡╨╖╨┤╨╡╨╗╨╕╨╜ ╨Ь╨╕╨╗╨░╨╜╨╛╨▓</span></em></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>╨Ш╨Ч╨б╨Ы╨Х╨Ф╨Т╨Р╨Э╨Х ╨Э╨Р ╨а╨Р╨С╨Ю╨в╨Р╨в╨Р ╨Э╨Р ╨Ь╨Р╨Ы╨Ю╨У╨Р╨С╨Р╨а╨Ш╨в╨Х╨Э ╨Ю╨С╨Х╨Ч╨Ъ╨а╨Ш╨Ы╨Ш╨в╨Х╨Ы ╨Ч╨Р ╨Ю╨С╨а╨Р╨С╨Ю╨в╨Ъ╨Р ╨Э╨Р ╨б╨Х╨Ь╨Х╨Э╨Р ╨Ю╨в<br>╨з╨Х╨а╨Х╨Э ╨С╨Ю╨а (PINUS NIGRA ARN.) ╨Ш ╨Ю╨С╨Ш╨Ъ╨Э╨Ю╨Т╨Х╨Э ╨б╨Ь╨к╨а╨з (PICEA ABIES KARST.) ......................................................................................................................................79<br></span><em><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">╨Ъ╨╛╨╜╤Б╤В╨░╨╜╤В╨╕╨╜ ╨Ь╨░╤А╨╕╨╜╨╛╨▓, ╨Ф╨╕╨╝╨╕╤В╤К╤А ╨Э╨╡╨╜╨╛╨▓, ╨б╨╛╤В╨╕╤А ╨У╨╗╤Г╤И╨║╨╛╨▓</span></em></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>╨Х╨Ъ╨б╨Я╨Х╨а╨Ш╨Ь╨Х╨Э╨в╨Р╨Ы╨Э╨Ш ╨Ь╨Х╨в╨Ю╨Ф╨Ш ╨Ч╨Р ╨Ш╨Ч╨б╨Ы╨Х╨Ф╨Т╨Р╨Э╨Х ╨Э╨Р ╨Х╨д╨Х╨Ъ╨в╨Р ╨Ю╨в ╨в╨а╨Ю╨Я╨Ю╨б╨д╨Х╨а╨Х╨Э ╨Ю╨Ч╨Ю╨Э ╨Т╨к╨а╨е╨г ╨У╨Ю╨а╨б- ╨Ъ╨Ш ╨Х╨Ъ╨Ю╨б╨Ш╨б╨в╨Х╨Ь╨Ш ...........................................................................................................97<br></span><em><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">╨Я╨╡╤В╤П ╨Я╤К╤А╨▓╨░╨╜╨╛╨▓╨░, ╨Э╨╕╨║╨╛╨╗╨╕╨╜╨░ ╨ж╨▓╨╡╤В╨║╨╛╨▓╨░, ╨б╨▓. ╨С╤А╨░╤В╨░╨╜╨╛╨▓╨░-╨Ф╨╛╨╜╤З╨╡╨▓╨░,╨а. ╨д╨╕╨║╨╛╨▓╨░, ╨б╨▓╨╡╤В╨╛╤Б╨╗╨░╨▓ ╨Р╨╜╨╡╨▓</span></em></span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">INVESTIGATIONS IN THE SILVER FIR (ABIES ALBA MILL.) ECOLOGICAL EXPERIMENTAL PROVENANCE<br>AND PROGENIE TRIALS ..................................................................................................11<br>Ivan Evtimov, Velitchko Gagov</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>FLORISTIC ELEMENTS AND BIOLOGICAL SPECTRUM OF FORESTS DOMINATED BY PUBESCENT OAK (QUERCUS PUBESCENS WILLD.) IN THE WEST FRONTIER MOUNTAINS .............................20<br></span><em><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Georgi Gogushev</span></em></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>RESTORATION OF BURNED FOREST AREAS ON THE TERRITORY OF SHIROKA LAKA AND VAILOVGRAD FORESTRY ENTERPRISES ...............................................................................................21<br></span><em><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Krasimira Petkova, Alexander Tashev, Latinka Topalova-Rzerzycha</span></em></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>ANALYSIS AND ASSESSMENT OF FOREST FIRES AND FIRE HAZARD .....................................................................................................................................46<br></span><em><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Kiril Lyubenov, Vladimir Konstantinov</span></em></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>ACID ROCK DRAINAGE FROM SUBSTRATA OF PB-ZN ORE PRODUCTION ....................................................................................................................................73<br></span><em><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\">Rossitsa Petrova</span></em></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"font-family: Tahoma;\"><br>PRODUCTIVITY OF FARM-REARED GREY PARTRID